Brute Force Demo

Create project folder:
mkdir brute-force-server
cd brute-force-server

Create virtual environment:
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate

Install FastAPI:
pip install "fastapi[standard]"

Run local server (inside lab12 folder):
fastapi dev main.py

Install Hydra:
sudo apt update
sudo apt install hydra

Run brute-force test:
hydra -f -I -V -L usernames.txt -P passwords.txt -s 8000 localhost http-form-post "/login:username=^USER^&password=^PASS^:F=Invalid"
